sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Mobile Device (User A)
    participant Loc as Location Service
    participant Cache as Latest-Loc Cache
    participant Hist as History Store
    participant ACL as Privacy / ACL
    participant Bus as Pub-Sub Bus
    participant Sub as Subscription Service
    participant F as Friend Device (User B)

    Note over Dev,F: LOCATION UPDATE + FAN-OUT
    Dev->>Dev: adaptive sample (10s driving / 30s walking / 5min still)
    Dev->>Loc: POST /location {lat, lng, ts}
    Loc->>Cache: SET loc:A (TTL 5min)
    opt history opt-in
        Loc-)Hist: append (user_id, ts, lat, lng)
    end
    Loc->>Bus: publish to topic user.location.A

    Bus-)Sub: deliver to subscribers of A
    loop each subscriber
        Sub->>ACL: check share permission (A -> subscriber)
        alt permitted AND within radius
            Sub->>Cache: get subscriber's loc
            Cache-->>Sub: subscriber loc
            Sub->>Sub: radius filter (haversine)
            Sub-)F: WS push location_update {A, lat, lng, ts}
        else denied or out of radius
            Note over Sub: drop publish for this pair
        end
    end

    Note over ACL,Sub: REVOCATION (immediate)
    ACL-)Sub: invalidation event (A revokes B)
    Sub->>Sub: drop (A,B) from in-memory routing table
